race.comment: THIS EAGLES A LEADER (1) finished out of the money two starts back then was beaten 2.25 lengths when seventh in a 366m contest at this track two-and-a-half weeks ago. Stepping up a level this time but on her best form she is capable of a big performance. LUMINOZITY (11) has not raced since he finished sixth over 320m at Retama Park on July 31. A bold showing is expected. NO MANDATES (9) turned in a strong run two starts ago at Prairie Meadows (Dirt) then failed to back it up over 320m at Prairie Meadows (Dirt) last time, beaten 3 lengths into sixth. Better suited at this shorter trip so is capable of a lot more this time. THE OUTLAW TORN (2) didn't do a bad job when fourth last start over 274m at this track. That followed a win at Gillespie County Fairground the start prior. In contention this time. Something for the Multiples: JESS ONE MORE KISS (7)
